After email archiving has been done in a particular space, there is no feature for these emails to be moved to another Space. This feature will be useful in scenarios where email archiving has been performed in an incorrect space involving a large number of emails.
A workaround to moving emails from one space to the other is:

1) Open the *SPACES* table and note down the *SPACEID* for the target (where the emails need to be moved to) space.
2) Edit the *CONTENT* table and execute the following query:
{noformat}
UPDATE CONTENT SET SPACEID = '<SpaceID of Target Space>' WHERE CONTENTTYPE = 'MAIL' AND TITLE = '<Email Subject for the email that has to be moved>'
{noformat}

